@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.03)) * 0.86)
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(tmp + 0.95) * (v2 + 0.10 * v1 + 0.45)))
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = v1
    v2 = 0.19
    tmp = v0
    tmp = (0.99 / tmp)
    v2 = 0.26
    data[tid] = v0
